# Bolha unblur +
Bolha unblur + extension unblurs bolha inactive Bolha adds.
It:
* Unblures the inactive add's page
* Allows you to still view add images
* Contact the seller

# Instlation
To install extension you first need to downoad the files. Go to code tab and press download zip.
<img src="https://private-user-images.githubusercontent.com/96793461/287520556-38c99d49-4b08-41dd-9708-d0c793faeb2a.png?jwt=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..70niACOyd9il4L-EUsBXEOAIA3aIwsTEH7YQS_iwdF4">
Then extract files (I use WinRar software in the explenation) to the folder where they will be stored. For example "C:\Users\User\Documents\Extensions"
<img src="https://private-user-images.githubusercontent.com/96793461/287520565-881a60e5-7d99-4279-8c34-3a94a0a52a21.png?jwt=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..4gzzE5PZdV3yVeyLLQGLosSJTSRgkrwG7-NAsCI1FsE">
After the files are extracted go to your browser (I use Google Chrome in the expenation, but it will be simmilar for other browsers), click extensions button and then manage extensions.
<img src="https://private-user-images.githubusercontent.com/96793461/287520567-9a346d82-fab5-436e-8647-041914976bc2.png?jwt=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..QXkuZrq1v5YdPwjErUt71dnG5KcfllFyjqTM-wdHk34">
Enambe developer mode.
<img src="https://private-user-images.githubusercontent.com/96793461/287520572-2206cf77-fa32-48ae-8f21-8d795c52bdae.png?jwt=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..Y8o0HjsA-axcPpPrf16dyWK94hNAWyQQJ1EtORJWrFQ">
Click load unpacked. And select the path to your extension's folder (the folder where you earlyer extracted the extension to)
<img src="https://private-user-images.githubusercontent.com/96793461/287520575-91a69efd-90a6-44e2-a5de-d67ed9bbd83d.png?jwt=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..KO2eA4X2ELm4BL_s3-VdHnsXGLQ1ZF2uc1Se3iTcfjQ">

# Update extension
Go to your browser (I use Google Chrome in the expenation, but it will be simmilar for other browsers), click extensions button and then manage extensions.
<img src="https://private-user-images.githubusercontent.com/96793461/287520567-9a346d82-fab5-436e-8647-041914976bc2.png?jwt=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..QXkuZrq1v5YdPwjErUt71dnG5KcfllFyjqTM-wdHk34">
Then click remove under the BolhaUnblur+ extension.
<img src="https://private-user-images.githubusercontent.com/96793461/287520580-0c57d10a-7617-4e23-a9b6-e1551a4204d9.png?jwt=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..c0xEOxdzahCBsoBoUitYkiomvTzamthsRjo8hXvDWm4">
Delete extension's source code from your comuter and the follow the [instalation](#instlation) process above.
